    "client_msg_id": "DB73DCBE-B0E3-4EF0-8263-138467D46F0E",
    "text": "Amazing! I will definitely add a link to the pod on the website :grin: \n\nCurrently on a code push to the main branch we identify the branch/path which has been affected by the push and identify that branch as potentially requiring more context. \n\nThere’s a lot more we can do with version control such as tagging branch states to commits and we’re always looking for angles. ",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1709300531.927509",
    "parent_user_id": "U065G31NJ7Q",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
