        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Amazing! I will definitely add a link to the pod on the website "
              },
              {
                "type": "emoji",
                "name": "grin",
                "unicode": "1f601"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " \n\nCurrently on a code push to the main branch we identify the branch/path which has been affected by the push and identify that branch as potentially requiring more context. \n\n"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "There’s"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " a lot more we can do with version control such as tagging branch states to commits and "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "we’re"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " always looking for angles. "
